snippet.title: Purgatory War of the Damned - Early Access Gameplay
snippet.description:
Purgatory is a fast-paced multiplayer fps game where you use a multitude of spells with a variety of effects to destroy your enemies.
Participate in duels, team battles or free-for-alls in the mysterious realm of purgatory, where all arenas have a history which chains them to this world.
